milestones.description: Hansie Cronje has broken the record for most sixes (8) in ODIs for SA, going past Peter Kirsten's 7
This is the highest match aggregate (459) involving teams Australia & South Africa in ODIs
Hansie Cronje and Jonty Rhodes's 106-run partnership is SA's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 105 between Peter Kirsten and Adrian Kuiper
Hansie Cronje has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (3) in ODIs for SA, going past Peter Kirsten's 2
